<title>Add or remove a contact</title>

  <p>To add a contact:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press <gui style="button">New</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>In the <gui>New contact</gui> window, enter the contact name and the
      desired information. Click on the menu next to each field to choose
      <gui>Work</gui>, <gui>Home</gui> or <gui>Other</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press <gui style="button">Create Contact</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p>To remove a contact:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Select the contact from your contact list.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press <gui style="button">Edit</gui> in the top-rigth corner of
      <app>Contacts</app>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press <gui style="button">Remove Contact</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

